.TH htmlex 1 "22 September, 2001" "Version @VERSION@" "User's Manual"
.SH NAME
htmlex \- a powerful hypertext markup language preprocessor
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B htmlex
.RI "[ " options " ] " file " [ " args " ] "
.br
.B htmlex
.RI "[ " options " ] [ " -- " [ " args " ] ] < " stdin
.SH COPYRIGHT
.B htmlex
is Copyright (C) 2001 by David A. Capello.
.br
This program was made in Argentina.
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBhtmlex\fR is a small but powerful \fBHTML\fR preprocesor, which you can have some
advantages relative to the conventional format of the \fB.html\fR files. Besides,
as htmlex is fully compatible with the standard \fBHTML\fR syntax, you can use any
\fBHTML\fR file that you have, and convert it to \fB.htex\fR.
.SH OPTIONS
\fBhtmlex\fP accepts the following options:
.TP
.B  --verbose
Print more information.
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Show summary of options.
.TP
.B \-v, \-\-version
Show version of program.

